<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Tu pedido fue despachado</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
    img { border: 0; outline: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; }
    a { text-decoration: none; }

    /* ── Dark mode ── */
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .bg-outer    { background-color: #1a1a1a !important; }
      .bg-card     { background-color: #222222 !important; }
      .bg-section  { background-color: #2d2d2d !important; }
      .bg-footer   { background-color: #1a1a1a !important; }
      .txt-main    { color: #e8e8e8 !important; }
      .txt-body    { color: #cccccc !important; }
      .txt-product { color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
      .txt-dim     { color: #888888 !important; }
      .divider     { border-top-color: #444444 !important; }
      .btn-track   { background-color: #3a3a3a !important; color: #e8e8e8 !important; }
      .btn-wp      { background-color: #3a3a3a !important; color: #e8e8e8 !important; }
    }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      /* Reduce card outer padding on mobile — matches original t186 mobile override */
      .card-outer { padding-left: 30px !important; padding-right: 30px !important; padding-bottom: 40px !important; }
      /* Logo column + image shrink to 80px on mobile — matches original t17 mobile override */
      .logo-col   { width: 80px !important; }
      .logo-img   { width: 80px !important; }
      /* Address columns: stack vertically */
      .addr-col-l { display: block !important; width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; padding: 20px 0 16px 0 !important; border-left: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd !important; }
      .addr-col-r { display: block !important; width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; padding: 16px 0 20px 0 !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-outer" style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#242424;font-family:Manrope,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="bg-outer" style="background-color:#242424;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:32px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width:100%;max-width:600px;">

          <!-- ── Main card ── -->
          <tr>
            <!--
              card-outer: padding:0 50px 60px 50px matches the original Tabular layout.
              All content rows inside inherit the 50px side gutters — no individual
              left/right padding needed on child cells.
            -->
            <td class="card-outer bg-card"
                style="background-color:#f8f8f8;padding:0 50px 60px 50px;">
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">

                <!-- ── Header: order id (left) + logo (right, flush top) ── -->
                <tr>
                  <!-- Text has top padding; logo has none — appears flush with card top -->
                  <td valign="top" style="padding:35px 12px 0 0;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;font-weight:700;color:#333333;" class="txt-main">Identificador de pedido</p>
                    <p style="margin:2px 0 0 0;font-size:15px;line-height:22px;font-weight:400;color:#555555;" class="txt-body"># {{ .OrderNumber }}</p>
                  </td>
                  <!-- Logo column: 127px wide, no padding → flush top-right within card gutters -->
                  <td class="logo-col" valign="top" width="127" style="width:127px;padding:0;vertical-align:top;">
                    <img class="logo-img"
                         src="https://storageapi.flockstore.co/fl-assets/assets/d0b1a4f5-7950-4aca-b1a1-535e98e1dc77-transcational_logo_covered.png"
                         alt="Flock Store" width="127"
                         style="display:block;width:127px;height:auto;border:0;" />
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── Greeting ── -->
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:28px 0 14px 0;">
                    <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:24px;line-height:30px;font-weight:700;color:#333333;" class="txt-main">Hola {{ .FirstName }},</h1>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── Body paragraphs ── -->
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:0 0 16px 0;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">Queremos contarte que hemos despachado tu pedido y, a partir de este momento, se encuentra en manos de la transportadora <strong style="color:#333333;" class="txt-main">{{ .CarrierName }}</strong>, con número de guía #<strong style="color:#333333;" class="txt-main">{{ .TrackingNumber }}</strong>.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:0 0 16px 0;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">A partir de este momento no se pueden realizar modificaciones a los datos de entrega de tu pedido.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:0 0 14px 0;">
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:24px;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">Puedes hacer seguimiento a tu pedido utilizando el siguiente enlace:</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── Track button ── -->
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:0 0 30px 0;">
                    <a href="{{ .TrackingURL }}" target="_blank" class="btn-track"
                       style="display:inline-block;padding:11px 22px;background-color:#f0f0f0;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#333333;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.4px;">RASTREAR PEDIDO</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>

                <!-- ── Product items ── -->
                {{ if .Items }}
                {{ range .Items }}
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:0 0 10px 0;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                           class="bg-section" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;border-radius:2px;">
                      <tr>
                        <td class="item-img-td" width="106" valign="middle"
                            style="padding:16px 8px 16px 16px;width:106px;">
                          {{ if .ImageURL }}
                          <img src="{{ .ImageURL }}" alt="{{ .ProductName }}" width="80"
                               style="display:block;width:80px;height:auto;max-height:120px;object-fit:cover;border:0;" />
                          {{ else }}
                          <div style="width:80px;height:80px;background:#dddddd;font-size:10px;color:#888;text-align:center;line-height:80px;">Sin imagen</div>
                          {{ end }}
                        </td>
                        <td valign="middle" style="padding:16px 16px 16px 8px;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 5px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:18px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;" class="txt-product">{{ .ProductName }}</p>
                          <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;font-weight:500;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">{{ .SKU }} - {{ .Variation }}</p>
                          <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;font-weight:500;color:#1a1a1a;border-top:1px solid #cccccc;padding-top:9px;" class="txt-product divider">CANTIDAD: {{ .Quantity }}</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                {{ end }}
                {{ end }}

                <!-- ── Addresses + payment ── -->
                <!--
                  No border-right between columns to avoid overflow artifacts on mobile Gmail.
                  Desktop: two columns side-by-side with gap via padding.
                  Mobile: addr-col-l / addr-col-r stack via display:block.
                -->
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding:4px 0 0 0;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"
                           class="bg-section" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;border-radius:2px;">
                      <tr>
                        <!-- Billing + payment -->
                        <td class="addr-col-l" valign="top" width="50%"
                            style="padding:28px 24px 28px 28px;box-sizing:border-box;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;" class="txt-product">Dirección de facturación</p>
                          <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;font-weight:500;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">
                            {{ .Billing.Name }}<br />
                            {{ .Billing.Address1 }}{{ if .Billing.Address2 }}<br />{{ .Billing.Address2 }}{{ end }}<br />
                            {{ .Billing.City }}, {{ .Billing.Department }}
                          </p>
                          <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;" class="txt-product">Método de pago</p>
                          <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;font-weight:500;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">{{ .PaymentMethod }}</p>
                        </td>
                        <!-- Shipping address -->
                        <td class="addr-col-r" valign="top" width="50%"
                            style="padding:28px 28px 28px 24px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left:1px solid #e0e0e0;">
                          <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a;" class="txt-product">Dirección de entrega</p>
                          <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;font-weight:500;color:#555555;" class="txt-body">
                            {{ .Shipping.Name }}<br />
                            {{ .Shipping.Address1 }}{{ if .Shipping.Address2 }}<br />{{ .Shipping.Address2 }}{{ end }}<br />
                            {{ .Shipping.City }}, {{ .Shipping.Department }}
                          </p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>

              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- ── Footer ── -->
          <tr>
            <!--
              bg-footer is always #242424. "Terminos y Condiciones" uses #aaaaaa
              (readable on dark bg, also survives if Gmail mobile strips the bg).
            -->
            <td class="bg-footer" style="padding:32px 50px;background-color:#242424;text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:Roboto,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:22px;font-weight:800;color:#757575;" class="txt-dim">¿Necesitas ayuda con tu pedido?</p>
              <a href="{{ .HelpURL }}" target="_blank" class="btn-wp"
                 style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background-color:#f3f3f3;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;font-weight:700;color:#333333;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.4px;">ESCRÍBENOS A WHATSAPP</a>
              <p style="margin:20px 0 0 0;font-family:Roboto,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#888888;">GRUPO COCCO SAS - Calle 18 Sur # 24D - 46. Esto es un correo electrónico automático; no recibirás respuesta al responderlo.</p>
              <p style="margin:8px 0 0 0;font-family:Roboto,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;">
                <a href="https://www.flockstore.co/terminos-condiciones/" target="_blank"
                   style="color:#aaaaaa;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;">Términos y Condiciones</a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
